item.title: Sudan's Civil War: An Inside Look with Ex-MI6 Chief
item.description: In this week's episode, One Decision hosts Kasia Madera and resident spymaster, former Chief of Britain's MI6, Sir Richard Dearlove, are joined by the New York Times Magazine staff writer Nicholas Casey to uncover the sober reality of the Sudanese civil war. Earlier this year, Casey was embedded with the Sudanese People's Movement Army, a rebel group fighting for democracy... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/NSR7393370733
